<li>Apple iPad Air (5th Generation) for $500 (was $599) at <a href="https://amzn.to/47EnYqW" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-orig-url="https://amzn.to/47EnYqW" data-ml-id="11" data-ml="true" data-xid="fr1700585771245ihb" data-uri="a40d0aa2e664ad57ae7913acb3f450a2">Amazon</a></li>
