<li>Apple iPad Mini (6th Generation) for $400 (was $499) at <a href="https://amzn.to/3G8yBGM" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-orig-url="https://amzn.to/3G8yBGM" data-ml-id="13" data-ml="true" data-xid="fr1700585771245fdf" data-uri="79990cf375b4ad53c750dd82754438bf">Amazon</a></li>
